NAME
    Hopkins::Plugin::RPC - SOAP interface to Hopkins

DESCRIPTION
    Hopkins::Plugin::RPC encapsulates the RPC (remote procedure call) POE
    session created by the manager session. this session uses the
    Server::SOAP component to provide a SOAP interface to the job server.

AUTHOR
    Mike Eldridge <diz@cpan.org>

